title: Good for multi tasking
description: I had a fully automatic washing machine. That will take ages to wash, but this machine is fast, & we get clean clothes. At the same time you can wash and dry clothes. Amazing product. I personally feel semi automatic machines are better than fully automatic. You can fill little water and wash clothes, but fully automatic needs water at particular level, If your area has water issues, you should never buy front loading fully automatic machine. Because it is very difficult to fill it. The only issue is difficulties in finding a cover for this...

No heater so make your purchase decision wisely.

title: Customer Service is not Responsive
description: I had ordered this product in Jan 2022 and I received a manufactured defect piece as the washing machine use to make a lot of noise and vibrate. When informed the technician he mentioned this is normal. When repetitively we called the technician then he confirmed the suspensions are spoiled and the machine was faulty in the beginning. Now the customer service doesn’t respond to your email, or do they have any person to get in touch to resolve your concern after sales service is pathetic. The biggest issue is the after sales service of this machine. I am still getting in touch with them since 3 months.

title: Bosch is good but Amazon in Eastern india is not good for big appliances
description: Bosch is nodoubt makes classy products but amazons partners are crooks they supplied me a damaged product so i order a replacement but it didnt arrived after 5 days then i called customer care and they told me our delivery partner said you denied replacement so we cant do anything now as it is a big appliance as per our rule you cant raise replacement again, they i asked them do you have any proof that i denied replacement if not then i will surely drag you to consumer court and even if you replace and again i got a damage or dented product i will replace again n again until i got a good product thanx god the replacement was good and running smoothly  and bosch service is also good, as per my knowledge if you live in south india you can go with amazon for big appliances but if you live in eastern part of india then allways go with flipkart for big appliances coz what i noticed is many complains from amazons west-bengal wear house what ever cm from that wb wearhouse specially big appliances are either faulty or physically damaged.

title: Must read before buying
description: So it all started after we purchased the whirlpool product froma Amazon.Prodcut got delivered within 2 days. Happy with fast delivery. Now started the actual struggle. I have included installation also in my cart while I ordered the machine. Now we waited for 2 days since we got an update that you will receive a a message containing details of oppointment time we did not receive any we call Amazon they say it has to be done from brand . 1st time We called up the whirlpool service support they said we have registered the complaint you get detail of installation in 2-3 hours. I did not receive any message so I called the service support 2nd time ,next day and to my surprise I got an update that there is no record of any complaint linked to the number I Sadi how come I kept calm and ask them to created another ticket . Waited for full day I did not receive any message call the support center again and heard the same response 'sir no complaint registered from your number' I did not keep the calm I said I don want any installation (it was already 4 days ) i was expecting atleast confirmation that they will assign anyone to install the product be it 3 Rd 4th or 5 th but this did not happened. I call the Amazon help desk and ask them to take the return they denied saying since it's just an installation issue but then I said if this doesn't not get resolved i will take it social media platform finally they agreed to take the return. Now i am returning the product just because of poor sevice of whirlpool. So think before investing if the initial service is poor how would it be after sale service . Kindly go for other brand like LG they take the responsibility of ther product .

title: Must read before buying
description: So it all started after we purchased the whirlpool product froma Amazon.Prodcut got delivered within 2 days. Happy with fast delivery. Now started the actual struggle. I have included installation also in my cart while I ordered the machine. Now we waited for 2 days since we got an update that you will receive a a message containing details of oppointment time we did not receive any we call Amazon they say it has to be done from brand . 1st time We called up the whirlpool service support they said we have registered the complaint you get detail of installation in 2-3 hours. I did not receive any message so I called the service support 2nd time ,next day and to my surprise I got an update that there is no record of any complaint linked to the number I Sadi how come I kept calm and ask them to created another ticket . Waited for full day I did not receive any message call the support center again and heard the same response 'sir no complaint registered from your number' I did not keep the calm I said I don want any installation (it was already 4 days ) i was expecting atleast confirmation that they will assign anyone to install the product be it 3 Rd 4th or 5 th but this did not happened. I call the Amazon help desk and ask them to take the return they denied saying since it's just an installation issue but then I said if this doesn't not get resolved i will take it social media platform finally they agreed to take the return. Now i am returning the product just because of poor sevice of whirlpool. So think before investing if the initial service is poor how would it be after sale service . Kindly go for other brand like LG they take the responsibility of ther product .

title: Good washing machine
description: Haier is the 5th washing machine we purchased. Our first washing machine was 6kg LG semi Automatic which we purchased in 2002. Later we switched to fully automatic top loading washing machines. Our next was Godrej, then Videocon later IFB and now Haier. We had ordered on 24th in Amazon and got delivered on 26th. Within 2 hours of Delivery, Haier team got in touch an in next few hours they came to install and demonstrated the features very nicely. This is the most silent machine we had so far. Very less vibration too. Wash quality is good and washes quickly and efficiently with less water compared to others we had used. If you have a budget of around 25k this is the best machine. We strongly recommend it!

title: It's an Fair deal for price + Brand + Look and Capacity
description: I got a valuable deal on amazone for price as compare to offline...superfast delivery and also installation done by within 24 hours by Llyod (Havells Brand)...Noise level is much better than any other brand Like IFB, LG and Samsung...Drum size is also a big ....Yes, look is superb bcoz of Black door with white color machine so white+black combination is good...it's an Fair deal for price + Brand + Look and Capacity...good thing is every company given 1000 RPM but Llyod is given 1400 RPM in this range....I am a first time buyer of washing machine..I think and see lots of companies and machine capacity and price then I find it the best way....in a starting I have a fear but when I actually see the machine and its work it's superb......Don't think too much just buy it..:)

title: Not so hardy for daily use. Poor service.
description: Using this after using a 6.5Kg. semi-automatic washing machine for 8 long years. So, have a pretty idea of using and care for same. Started giving trouble after 6 months of using. The wash tumbler either rotates in one direction or sometimes nither rotates at all. Though already opted for extended warranty. Had to raise a complain, service personnel visited but could not fix due to not having required spares then. And didn't turned up after that even after lapse of at least 15days of visit. The company never checks with the customer whether their issues are resolved or not.
